title: Casey Aylward from Astronoid
itunes:title: Casey Aylward from Astronoid
description:
Boom! NEW FAVORITE BAND ALERT! Before you listen to this podcast, please listen to Astronoid’s LP entitled “Air” and you will thank me. Then, come back and listen to this insightful discussion between myself and Casey Aylward from Astronoid/Vatnett Viskar. We get in depth on what it’s like to be a mid-level touring band, the promise of a bright future and tour life in general. Love it! Use our Amazon Affiliate Code to support the show!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
